      ],
      "footnotes": []
    },
    {
      "section": "ENTRY_003 — Operational Procedures",
      "desc": "Memory as structure",
      "passage": "Memory is not storage. Memory is structure. When the structure fails, the building does not empty — it collapses.",
      "passage_short": "Memory is not storage. Memory is structure. When",
      "glyphs": [
        {
          "glyph": "echo",
          "size": 6,
          "stage": 0,
          "late": false
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [
        {
          "n": 40,
          "text": "Looked at my Locked Memory of the rain on asphalt. The words have been scratched out. In their place, someone — not me — has written: THE SKY IS A SHROUD.",
          "act": 4,
          "late": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "section": "ENTRY_003 — Operational Procedures",
      "desc": "Memory System (Scars)",
      "passage": "MEMORY SYSTEM — Five Active Scars (+2 bonus), three Fading Scars (+1 bonus), one Core Scar (+3 bonus — costs 3 Coherence to maintain).",
      "passage_short": "MEMORY SYSTEM — Five Active Scars (+2 bonus),",
      "glyphs": [],
      "footnotes": [
        {
          "n": 41,
          "text": "Rose is right. The memories were anchors dragging us down. Stopped using a pen. The needle leaves a cleaner mark.",
          "act": 4,
          "late": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "section": "ENTRY_003 — Operational Procedures",
      "desc": "Paying the Tax",
      "passage": "When you succeed with DISRUPT (any result), roll d6. On 3-6: no tax this time. On 1-2: pay the Tax.",
      "passage_short": "When you succeed with DISRUPT (any result), roll",
      "glyphs": [],
      "footnotes": [
        {
          "n": 42,
          "text": "Tried to skip the Violence Tax after a messy scene. Woke up with a small circular bruise on my inner wrist. Exactly where the Tax tracker prints on the sheet.",
          "act": 4,
          "late": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "section": "ENTRY_003 — Operational Procedures",
      "desc": "Holding Actions (Alan's revisit)",
      "passage": "I never took Holding Actions for the first 200 years. Not because I didn't want to. Because I convinced myself they didn't matter.",
      "passage_short": "I never took Holding Actions for the first",
      "glyphs": [
        {
          "glyph": "burden",
          "size": 6,
          "stage": 0,
          "late": false
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": []
    },
