    {
      "section": "ENTRY_006 — Terminal Configurations",
      "desc": "Alan's closing message",
      "passage": "FROM ALAN ROSE — Chen's wrong about almost everything. But her heart's in the right place. I wanted you to know that before...",
      "passage_short": "FROM ALAN ROSE — Chen's wrong about almost",
      "glyphs": [],
      "footnotes": [
        {
          "n": 48,
          "text": "Rose just told me Chen has been wrong about almost everything. I think he is lying to be kind. I think she has been right and that is the problem.",
          "act": 4,
          "late": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "section": "Alan on Zaaken",
      "desc": "the Zaaken passage",
      "passage": "Zaaken wasn't always Zaaken. He had a name. I remember the first two letters and the shape of how his friends said it.",
      "passage_short": "Zaaken wasn't always Zaaken. He had a name.",
      "glyphs": [],
      "footnotes": [
        {
          "n": 49,
          "text": "He remembers two letters of a friend's name. I have stopped trying to remember Saul's. Maybe he was always mine.",
          "act": 5,
          "late": false
        }
      ]
    },
